name: HEN WavyPunk #1 (Limited Edition)
description:
WavyPunks are 1/1 3D Voxel Heads that are made to be worn on your Avatars in Cryptovoxels. This is the 1st piece of the HEN WavyPunks (Limited Edition) collection that will be exclusively designed & created by artist 1OF1NEO

This NFT will included a GIF File, Vox (Wearable) Airdropped to your Wallet & a PFP (Headshot)
